def plotGene(myGeneSym):#myGeneSym = "ARG1"
    metaGene = fc[fc.myGeneSym == myGeneSym].drop_duplicates(['gpl','gse','subset'])
    metaGene.title = myGeneSym
    m = getMetaAnalysisFromR(metaGene)
    %R -i m -w 750 -h 500 forest(m, pred=T)

def showGene(myGeneSym):
    plotGene(myGeneSym)
    return (combinedFixed.ix[[myGeneSym]] if combinedRandom.ix[[myGeneSym]].empty else combinedRandom.ix[[myGeneSym]])[biomarkerCols] 

def showNcbi(myGeneSym):
    return show_iframe('http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/gene/?term=(' \
                       + myGeneSym \
                       + '%5Bsym%5D)+AND+%22Homo+sapiens%22%5Bporgn%3A__txid9606%5D')
